                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen ammonia energy storage system based on Carnot cell and ammonia adsorption separation",
                    "一种基于卡诺电池和氨吸附分离的氢氨储能系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a hydrogen-ammonia energy storage system based on a Carnot cell and ammonia adsorption separation. Comprising a photovoltaic power generation unit, a solar heat collection unit, a Carnot cell unit, a water electrolysis hydrogen production unit, an air separation nitrogen production unit, an ammonia synthesis unit and an ammonia adsorption unit. The photovoltaic power generation unit is connected with a heat pump of the Carnot cell unit, the solar heat collection unit is connected with the heat pump of the Carnot cell unit, power provided by the Carnot cell unit is connected with the water electrolysis hydrogen production unit, power provided by the Carnot cell unit is connected with the air separation nitrogen production unit, and the air separation nitrogen production unit is connected with the air separation nitrogen production unit. The hydrogen output end of the water electrolysis hydrogen production unit is connected with the ammonia synthesis unit, the nitrogen output end of the electric air separation nitrogen production unit is connected with the ammonia synthesis unit, and the product gas output end of the ammonia synthesis unit is connected with the input end of the ammonia adsorption system. The renewable energy storage mode is improved, the stability of the system is enhanced, the product purity is improved, the energy consumption of the system is reduced, and the energy storage cost of the system is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种基于卡诺电池和氨吸附分离的氢氨储能系统。包括光伏发电单元、太阳能集热单元、卡诺电池单元、电解水制氢单元、空分制氮单元、合成氨单元以及氨吸附单元。所述光伏发电单元与卡诺电池单元的热泵相连接，所述太阳能集热单元与卡诺电池单元的热泵相连接，所述卡诺电池单元提供的电力与电解水制氢单元相连接，所述卡诺电池单元提供的电力与空分制氮单元相连接，所述电解水制氢单元的氢气输出端与合成氨单元相连接，所述电空分制氮单元的氮气输出端与合成氨单元相连接，所述合成氨单元的产品气输出端与氨吸附系统的输入端相连接。本发明改进可再生能源储能方式，增强系统的稳定性，提高产品纯度，降低了系统能耗，降低系统储能成本。"
                }
            ]
